    <ol>
      <li>
        <p>Sample responses: </p>
        <ol>
        <li>3 by 4 rectangle</li>
        <li>4 by 6 rectangle</li>
        <li>6 by 3 rectangle</li>
        <li>7 by 4 rectangle</li>
        <li>3 by 2 rectangle</li>
        </ol>
      </li>
      <li>Sample response: You can think about the rows as groups and the number of rows as the number of groups. When you multiply these numbers, it gives you the total number of squares.</li>
    </ol>
